column2: select so.bossprimary, so.sdssprimary, sp.specObjID, sp.objid, so.mjd, so.plate, so.fiberID, so2.mjd as mjd2, so2.plate as plate2, so2.fiberID as fiberID2, so.ra, so2.ra as ra2, so.dec, so2.dec as dec2, sp.ra as raSP, sp.dec as decSP, sp.z, so.z_noqso, so.zErr_noqso, sp.class, sp.subclass, so.class_noqso, so.subclass_noqso, so.class_person, so2.class as class2, so2.subclass as subclass2, so.programname, so.instrument, so2.instrument as instrument2, so.survey, so.scienceprimary, so.zwarning, so2.zwarning as zwarning2, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak, f.integr, f.rms into mydb.MyTable from SpecObjAll AS so JOIN SpecObjAll as so2 ON so.bestObjId = so2.bestObjId JOIN SpecPhoto as sp ON sp.specobjid = so.specobjid JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > # and so.instrument ! = so2.instrument
